e="color:black"><span style="font-size:10.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">(I told him phases involved in Software development life cycle (SDLC). I didn&rsquo;t know all of them so told some of them) </span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:10.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">5. What is Automata Theory? Give an example. </span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:10.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">6. What is XML Parsing? </span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:10.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">7. What is abstract and mutable keyword? </span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:10.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">8. Suppose that I am your manager. What will you do if I give you a boring project to do? </span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:10.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">(6 students were selected for the HR round) </span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-