(49, 'Walmart Labs by Arpit Uppal', '09-28-17', 'akki', 'walmartlabs-logo.jpg', 'Walmart,Walmart Labs,interview,experience,internship', '<p style="margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif">&nbsp;<strong><span style="font-size:20.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">Walmart Labs Interview Experience (on campus) </span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">1</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:8.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">st </span></span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">round(Written Test)- </span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">It was an online test of 90 minutes and was conducted on Hackerearth. It consisted of 10 MCQ&rsquo;s and 3 coding questions. MCQ&rsquo;s consisted of general aptitude questions, questions related to networking, programming etc and very easy. </span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">The coding questions were as follows: </s